OL,3,CPlans to introduce tourism tax in
OL,4,CWales reach crucial stage today
OL,6,FPlans to introduce a tourism tax in
OL,7,FWales will reach a crucial stage today
OL,8,F(1 July) with the proposals facing a
OL,9,Fpivotal vote in the Senedd.
OL,11,FMembers of the Senedd will vote on the
OL,12,FVisitor Levy Bill, which would give
OL,13,Fcouncils the power to charge people
OL,14,Ffor overnight stays in tourist
OL,15,Faccommodation.
OL,17,FIf approved, the charge could be up to
OL,18,F#1.30 per person, per night, depending
OL,19,Fon the type of accommodation.
