OL,3,CPlans to introduce tourism tax in
OL,4,CWales reach crucial stage today
OL,6,FThe bill is currently at the third
OL,7,Fstage in the Senedd and if it passes,
OL,8,Fit would then likely be rubber-stamped
OL,9,Flater this month before being sent to
OL,10,Fthe King for Royal Assent.
OL,12,FEven then, councils would not be
OL,13,Frequired to bring in the charge - but
OL,14,Fthey will have the power to do so from
OL,15,F2027.
OL,17,FThe Welsh Government says the levy
OL,18,Fcould raise around #33 million a year
OL,19,Fif adopted by local authorities across
OL,20,FWales.
