OL,6,FWhat are the arguments for the tourism
OL,7,Ftax?
OL,9,FSome supporters say it would help fund
OL,10,Finfrastructure and local services in
OL,11,Ftourist hotspots, including the upkeep
OL,12,Fof footpaths, public toilets and waste
OL,13,Fcollections.
OL,15,FJenny Swarbrick, who runs a
OL,16,Fregenerative farm with visitor
OL,17,Faccommodation in Eryri National Park,
OL,18,Fbacks the idea.
